    static WeightedRandomList<MobSpawnSettings.SpawnerData>
    StructureSpawnManager.getStructureSpawns​(StructureFeatureManager structureManager, MobCategory classification, BlockPos pos)
    Looks up if a given position is within a structure and returns any entity spawns that structure has for the given classification, or null if none are found.
